Description: I have installed Endpoint protector 6.2.2 in my windows 10 device, i need to unintall it.
When i try to uninstall using MSI product code its asking to close some applications i have closed and tried its not uninstalling properly
What We've Learned Updated: We have sent the necessary steps for uninstalling the epp client on Windows computers.
Next Steps Updated: If the customer still encounters issues with uninstalling, we'll schedule a remote session.
